processors.body:
We do not sell your data and do not pass it to third parties for marketing. Technically, your data is processed by the infrastructure providers we rely on:

— Supabase (database storage for inquiries and content);
— Resend (email notifications sent to property@alabproperty.com);
— Telegram (internal alerts to ALAB managers about a new inquiry).

Each processor only receives the minimum data required for its specific task.

rights.body:
With respect to your personal data, you can:

— request a copy of the data we hold about you;
— ask us to correct inaccurate data;
— ask us to delete your data;
— withdraw consent to further processing.

To exercise any of these rights, please write to us and we will respond within a reasonable time.
